title: The Double Eagle Has Landed!
itunes:title: The Double Eagle Has Landed!
description: Today on The Cigar Authority Dave Garofalo, Mr Jonathan and Chuck Morrison smoke the new Double Eagle from Hammer & Sickle, create some controversy with The Lady of The Stick, and meet a 22 year old Cigarlebrity in-the-making with his new release of Tosa. The boys also talk about new releases & everything cigar. It's time for the finer things in life... It's time for The Cigar Authority.
